	   <tr><td colspan=2>I personally like to play human (since i like to drag myself in the game and play the game) But human do not make powerfull paladin. My opinion the best paladin is high elf. with 85agil as base (at higher level agil take part on your AC.. and you always want more AC) 100wis base, 90 int and 90cha.. Its the powerleader of starting character. Dont have to worry too much on str or sta.. str item always easy to get, sta item so too.. which wont make a lot of difference anyway, since at higher level having about 200more hp than nextdoor paly wont make you better A LOT and enable you to kick someones butt. <br><br>My character is human paladin. Has 90str 80sta 80agil 75dex 90wis 85cha as base. Dispute downside bring night blind, my paladin can stand toe to toe against ranger, mage, necro, and warrior.. yes.. warrior (thank goodness he dont have regen BP when fighting me.. i would get pummeled if he has one)<br><br>So play what you want and learn every curve of your paladin skill.. your character stat is 3rd, character skill is 2nd, and YOUR skill is 1st :)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
